  <official_title>Tolerance and Resistance to Ibrutinib in Patients With Chronic Lymphocytic Leukemia (CLL): Analysis of Real-life Data: &quot;Snapshot&quot; at 3 Years From the End of Ibrutinib ATU. A National Study of the FILO-LLC Group</official_title>
